#### `GET /api/news/breaking`
Breaking news ticker тАФ returns array of `id` and `title` only.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "OK",
  "data": [
    { "id": 3, "title": "Breaking: Senate Passes New Bill" },
    { "id": 7, "title": "Markets Hit Record High" }
  ]
}
```

---

#### `GET /api/news/articles?tab={tab}&page={page}&limit={limit}`
Latest Stories section with tab filtering and pagination.

| Param | Default | Options |
|-------|---------|---------|
| `tab` | `latest` | `latest`, `think`, `health` |
| `page` | `1` | any number |
| `limit` | `4` | any number |

**Examples:**
```
GET /api/news/articles
GET /api/news/articles?tab=think
GET /api/news/articles?tab=health
GET /api/news/articles?page=2&limit=4
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "OK",
  "data": {
    "articles": [...],
    "pagination": {
      "currentPage": 1,
      "totalPages": 5,
      "totalItems": 20,
      "limit": 4
    }
  }
}
```

