### ЁЯУД Detail Page

#### `GET /api/news/:id`
Full article detail.

| Status | Case |
|--------|------|
| `200` | Article found |
| `400` | ID is not a number (e.g. `/api/news/abc`) |
| `404` | Article not found (e.g. `/api/news/999`) |

**Error response:**
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Article not found with id: 999",
  "data": null
}
```

---

#### `GET /api/news/:id/related`
Related articles from the same category (excludes current article). Returns max 5 articles.

